{"tid":2200312,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透有圖]我敢講今集刀劍神域已經成功反cup","createTime":"2020-09-13T00:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T08:29:04.000Z","uid":57911,"like":37,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1e41d502084c1662af5fa4e31e3cd263b3843066","tid":2200312,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:00:25.000Z","msg":"我手上得幾張低清圖希望大家唔好介意<br />\n我就用幾張圖同大家講刀劍神域今集係點樣反cup<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/13/074022_5750fb0bd37c32c008739398c3f536a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F13%2F074022_5750fb0bd37c32c008739398c3f536a8.png&h=d0388b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學妹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/13/074110_e7897dc8c97efcf93fa604b2319c22fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F13%2F074110_e7897dc8c97efcf93fa604b2319c22fb.png&h=b962331f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/13/074145_30104bcf00923d8b44c65c4a66700173.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F13%2F074145_30104bcf00923d8b44c65c4a66700173.png&h=648998cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回憶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/13/074253_7ef1fc9b3eebd6d6bdbc3fe975b1ed65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F13%2F074253_7ef1fc9b3eebd6d6bdbc3fe975b1ed65.png&h=baefe779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n痛苦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/13/074332_5a7731a12bf15e69ea0e49c53df35da7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F13%2F074332_5a7731a12bf15e69ea0e49c53df35da7.png&h=067a445f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更重要嘅係作者竟然仲記得嗰個善良又孤獨嘅真男人<br />\n<br />\n大家望下嗰個孤獨嘅身影，好似期待著某日可以再同嗰個天降落嚟同自己相同髮型嘅女仔相遇<br />\n<br />\n肥豬喺依場大戰失去咗豬女，失去咗天降嘅女仔<br />\n<br />\n嗰個背後嘅劇情係唔係同前面某個同一集失戀兩次嘅傻豬女主好相似<br />\n<br />\n所以話連官方都承認莉法同肥豬天生一對<br />\n到咗莉法再入返UW世界<br />\n肥豬已經唔再存在<br />\n希望到時莉法UW個帳號仲保留住肥豬嘅後代<br />\n延續肥豬嘅思念"},{"pid":"ec84f6dc1961f35f18b1c656bfaa6dbfd61bee2e","tid":2200312,"uid":145928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:02:45.000Z","msg":"又係你"},{"pid":"b85a02c95a8455dd130caef298d550a69837652b","tid":2200312,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd74ab44f17734a9910bdfd549ac75c65192a19","tid":2200312,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />高汁"},{"pid":"c6ccfaf2a5f6c2323d181f93d962bb58a1f2c433","tid":2200312,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5026fd117de8834ad35021eb3a5a944e35c3cabc","tid":2200312,"uid":18672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e41d502084c1662af5fa4e31e3cd263b3843066","tid":2200312,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T00:00:25.000Z","msg":"我手上得幾張低清圖希望大家唔好介意<br />\n我就用幾張圖同大家講刀劍神域今集係點樣反cup<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/13/074022_5750fb0bd37c32c008739398c3f536a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u